OL,6,FLabour, Lib Dem and Conservative
OL,7,Fpoliticians from the South clash over
OL,8,Fthe government's plans to overhaul the
OL,9,Fbenefits system on ITV Meridian's The
OL,10,FLast Word
OL,12,FThe increasing number of people
OL,13,Fclaiming health-related benefits is
OL,14,F"not sustainable", according to a
OL,15,Fsenior Labour MP.
