OL,3,CBenefits system 'not sustainable',
OL,4,Csenior Labour MP claims
OL,6,FAnneliese Dodds told ITV Meridian's
OL,7,FThe Last Word: "If we continue on
OL,8,Fcurrent trends, we will see a doubling
OL,9,Fof the number of people claiming
OL,10,F(personal independence payment) by the
OL,11,Fend of the decade."
OL,13,FThe Oxford East MP's comments come
OL,14,Fafter the government published its
OL,15,Fcontroversial proposals to reform
OL,16,Flarge parts of the welfare system.
OL,18,FThe Universal Credit and Personal
OL,19,FIndependence Payment Bill is due to be
OL,20,Fvoted on in Parliament next month.
