OL,3,CBenefits system 'not sustainable',
OL,4,Csenior Labour MP claims
OL,6,FDozens of Labour MPs are understood to
OL,7,Fbe preparing to rebel and vote against
OL,8,Fthe changes, which are aimed at saving
OL,9,Fup to #5 billion a year.
OL,11,FPoole Labour MP Neil Duncan-Jordan has
OL,12,Faccused ministers of "rushing" the
OL,13,Freforms and said they aren't something
OL,14,Fhe's "prepared to support".
OL,16,FThe bill ` aimed at encouraging more
OL,17,Fpeople off sickness benefits and into
OL,18,Fwork ` includes the tightening of
OL,19,Fcriteria for personal independence
OL,20,Fpayment.
