OL,3,CBenefits system 'not sustainable',
OL,4,Csenior Labour MP claims
OL,6,FThe vast majority of current claimants
OL,7,Fwould continue to be eligible for the
OL,8,Fbenefit ` known as Pip ` according to
OL,9,FMs Dodds.
OL,11,FConservative Dame Penny Mordaunt told
OL,12,FITV Meridian's monthly politics
OL,13,Fprogramme: "Labour did not have any
OL,14,Fplans in their manifesto around this
OL,15,Fissue at all.
OL,17,F"They're now in trouble with their
OL,18,FMPs. Had all their MPs stood on that
OL,19,Fplatform, they'd find it easier to
OL,20,Fconvince them to go through the voting
OL,21,Flobbies."
