OL,3,CBenefits system 'not sustainable',
OL,4,Csenior Labour MP claims
OL,6,FThe former Portsmouth North MP added:
OL,7,F"When you approach these issues purely
OL,8,Fabout saving money, you end up making
OL,9,Fbad decisions and causing anxiety for
OL,10,Fpeople."
OL,12,FThe latest data showed more than 3.7
OL,13,Fmillion people in England and Wales
OL,14,Fclaim Pip.
OL,16,FAn impact assessment published
OL,17,Falongside the welfare bill confirmed
OL,18,Fthe changes to Pip entitlement rules
OL,19,Fcould see about 800,000 people lose
OL,20,Ftheir benefit.
